name: Nysad
Lore: 'Kajain''sa''Nikto. Fiercely loyal to Jabba. Stands guard over the sail barge during the Hutt''s many trips to Mos Eisley.',
Text: 'Deploys only on Tatooine. May deploy as a ''react'' to a Jabba''s Palace site or aboard a vehicle at a Tatooine site. Power +3 when defending a battle at a Jabba''s Palace site.',
